Summary: object moved fast from the right to the lest with no sound and only reflective light
divs: Sighting Detailsabout 6 45 pm to 6 50 pm I went outside in the back yard to throw out the trash. As I was walking to the bin area, I notice something out of place moving fast in the sky. First imprison, I said to myself look at that bird flying. Next, I said it's moving very fast and it dark out. As it moved I noticed only the reflection from the moon on top and on the bottom it was darker then the regular night sky. I lost sight of it when it reached a place in the sky where there was more light noise.
